{
  "stem": "14900.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And shortly after I had encountered this SS man in the German girl's home, here I'm walking past the church on the sidewalk with, fortunately for me, a dead chicken inside the basket with a napkin over it.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If it had been live and gone 'bawk, bawk, bawk' I would have been dead on the spot, probably.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And here comes the SS man-- he was the head honcho in Lubranetz-- towards me on the sidewalk.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "A, I'm a Jew walking on the sidewalk, carrying a forbidden dead chicken, not wearing a star.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I didn't know what to do, so I just kept the pace up and kept walking.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we're maybe 10 feet apart, maybe less.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he goes heil Hitler to me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Took me a split second, I went heil Hitler, smiled, and kept walking the same pace.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Again, it was forbidden for Jews to say heil Hitler.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But I knew if I didn't, it was really dangerous.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So I just took a chance on it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "At the same pace went home, my mother took one look at my face after I got in.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "She asked what happened.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I never went to the butcher's again.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And somehow or other, I never played in the German girl's home again either.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So I don't know how that was resolved.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But back to the departure of my father that happened, I think, June one or two, first week of June '41.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Things got worse and worse.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And we were already living in one half of our two bedroom apartment, which was a mansion by Polish country standards.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Polish Catholic couple were occupying the other half.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And my grandparents lived with us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We had to narrow down to one room, because there was no way to heat the place.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
